           <p style="margin:0px 10px;font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>朝代：</span><span style="padding-left:4px;">唐代</span></p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px;font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>作者：</span><span style="padding-left:4px;"><a href="/shiren/415_1.html" target="_blank">温庭筠</a></span>
           </p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>类型：</span>
           <span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_1_1_0_0.html">写景</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_27_1_0_0.html">抒情</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_313_1_0_0.html">哀怨</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_276_1_0_0.html">愁绪</a></span></p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>原文：</span></p>
           <p></p><p>竹风轻动庭除冷，珠帘月上玲珑影。山枕隐秾妆，绿檀金凤凰。</p><p>两蛾愁黛浅，故国吴宫远。春恨正关情，画楼残点声。</p><p></p>
