           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>类型：</span>
           <span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_3_1_0_0.html">春天</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_1_1_0_0.html">写景</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_27_1_0_0.html">抒情</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_279_1_0_0.html">寂寞</a></span></p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>原文：</span></p>
           <p></p><p>南园满地堆轻絮，愁闻一霎清明雨。雨后却斜阳，杏花零落香。</p><p>无言匀睡脸，枕上屏山掩。时节欲黄昏，无憀独倚门。</p><p></p>
