           <p style="margin:0px 10px;font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>朝代：</span><span style="padding-left:4px;">唐代</span></p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px;font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>作者：</span><span style="padding-left:4px;"><a href="/shiren/415_1.html" target="_blank">温庭筠</a></span>
