           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>类型：</span>
           <span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_1_1_0_0.html">写景</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_27_1_0_0.html">抒情</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_89_1_0_0.html">孤独</a></span></p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>原文：</span></p>
           <p></p><p>翠翘金缕双鸂鶒，水纹细起春池碧。池上海棠梨，雨晴红满枝。</p><p>绣衫遮笑靥，烟草粘飞蝶。青琐对芳菲，玉关音信稀。</p><p></p>
