           <p style="margin:0px 10px;font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>朝代：</span><span style="padding-left:4px;">宋代</span></p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px;font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>作者：</span><span style="padding-left:4px;"><a href="/shiren/183_1.html" target="_blank">苏轼</a></span>
           </p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>类型：</span>
           <span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_1_1_0_0.html">写景</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_8_1_0_0.html">写雪</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_27_1_0_0.html">抒情</a></span><span class="scmk"><a style="margin-right:5px;" target="_blank" href="tags_269_1_0_0.html">乐观</a></span></p>
           <p style="margin:0px 10px; font-size:12px;line-height:160%;"><span>原文：</span></p>
           <p></p><p>门外山光马亦惊，阶前屐齿我先行。</p><p>风花误入长春苑，云月长临不夜城。</p><p>未许牛羊伤至洁，且看鸦鹊弄新晴。</p><p>更须携被留僧榻，待听催檐泻竹声。</p><p></p>
